Package: work.tkgstrator.piyoshot
Name: PiyoShot
Version: 0.1.0
Architecture: iphoneos-arm64
Description: PiyoShogi capture tweak. Reads a SFEN + hash JSONL, drives the in-app parseSFEN via a Dobby-hooked trampoline, redraws ShogiBoardView, and snapshots the board / key window into <sandbox>/Documents/piyo_captures/<hash>_{board,screen}.png. Runs entirely client-side: never touches the network, never mutates account state. For authorized research use only.
Maintainer: NEVER KNOWS BEST
Author: tkgstrator
Section: Tweaks
Depends: mobilesubstrate
